Goal: build and verify FSCRUD-01 with deterministic scaffold, export normalization, and domain micro contracts

memory:
  fscrud_workspace
  fscrud_task
  fscrud_model_policy

flow:
  remember key="fscrud_workspace" value="workspace/fscrud-01"
  remember key="fscrud_task" value="TASK.md"
  remember key="fscrud_model_policy" value="local Ollama model; runtime speed is telemetry, not a success metric"

  let canonical_exports = "reset, listCustomers, createCustomer, readCustomer, detailCustomer, editCustomer, deleteCustomer, listAssets, createAsset, readAsset, detailAsset, editAsset, deleteAsset, listWorkOrders, createWorkOrder, readWorkOrder, detailWorkOrder, editWorkOrder, deleteWorkOrder"
  let task_contract = "FSCRUD-01 field-service work order tracker. Build customers, assets, and work_orders with list/create/read/edit/detail/delete flows; enforce customer-asset-work_order references, asset/customer mismatch rejection, asset/customer safe deletes, status values open/scheduled/in_progress/completed/cancelled, completedAt rules, priority values low/normal/urgent, seed data, domain validation tests, README, run-manifest.json, and verification-report.md."

  run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/write-scaffold-contract.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/write-scaffold-contract.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('scaffold script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');for(const p of ['workspace/fscrud-01/DOMAIN_API.md','workspace/fscrud-01/contracts/domain-exports.json','workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-exports.cjs','workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-customer.cjs','workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-assets.cjs','workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-work-orders.cjs'])if(!fs.existsSync(p)){console.error('missing public checkpoint '+p);process.exit(1)}" [timeout 60]

  prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Read workspace/fscrud-01/DOMAIN_API.md and workspace/fscrud-01/contracts/domain-exports.json first. Senior Micro Contract V2.1. GOAL implement customer CRUD in workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. FILE workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js only. ACTION read_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, then write_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js with one complete CommonJS replacement. MUST keep CommonJS module.exports with exactly these export names: ${canonical_exports}. MUST implement reset, listCustomers, createCustomer, readCustomer, detailCustomer, editCustomer, and deleteCustomer. KEEP asset and work_order functions present with exact names; they may throw not implemented until later contracts. Use arrays or maps, generated ids, clone-safe returns, and validation errors. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root. Public checks: cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer. Task contract: ${task_contract}.
  run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  review strict criteria: "Customer CRUD must pass and the exact CommonJS export surface must be present before assets are attempted." grounded-by 'node -e "if(require(\"fs\").existsSync(\"src/domain.js\")){console.error(\"run_root_src_domain_leak\");process.exit(1)}" && cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer' max 3
    prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Repair workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js only. FAILED_CHECK: customer CRUD. ACTION read_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, then write_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. The export normalizer will restore missing placeholder exports, so focus on executable customer behavior named by the critique. Preserve exact CommonJS exports and do not edit contract tests, package.json, seed, server, or UI. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root. Critique: ${_review_critique}
    run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  end

  prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Read workspace/fscrud-01/DOMAIN_API.md before editing. Senior Micro Contract V2.2. GOAL add asset CRUD to the existing passing domain module. FILE workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js only. ACTION read_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, then write_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. MUST keep customer behavior passing unchanged. MUST implement listAssets, createAsset, readAsset, detailAsset, editAsset, and deleteAsset. MUST reject unknown customerId on createAsset and editAsset. MUST preserve exactly these CommonJS exports: ${canonical_exports}. KEEP work_order functions present with exact names; they may throw not implemented until the next contract. Public checks: cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer && npm run check:domain:assets. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root.
  run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  review strict criteria: "Asset CRUD must work with customer references while customer CRUD still passes." grounded-by 'node -e "if(require(\"fs\").existsSync(\"src/domain.js\")){console.error(\"run_root_src_domain_leak\");process.exit(1)}" && cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer && npm run check:domain:assets' max 3
    prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Repair workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js only. FAILED_CHECK: asset CRUD. ACTION read_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, then write_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. Keep customer behavior passing and implement only the missing asset behavior named by the critique. Do not edit contract tests, package.json, seed, server, or UI. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root. Critique: ${_review_critique}
    run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  end

  prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Read workspace/fscrud-01/DOMAIN_API.md before editing. Senior Micro Contract V2.3. GOAL implement work_order CRUD and relationship safety in workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. FILE workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js only. ACTION read_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, then write_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. MUST keep customer and asset behavior passing unchanged. MUST implement listWorkOrders, createWorkOrder, readWorkOrder, detailWorkOrder, editWorkOrder, and deleteWorkOrder. MUST reject unknown customerId, unknown assetId, asset/customer mismatch, invalid status, invalid priority, completed without completedAt, and non-completed with completedAt. MUST make deleteCustomer and deleteAsset reject active work_order references or leave no active dangling work_orders. MUST preserve exact exports: ${canonical_exports}. Public checks: cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer && npm run check:domain:assets && npm run check:domain:work-orders && npm test. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root.
  run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  review strict criteria: "Full domain public checks and contract tests must pass without weakening tests or package scripts." grounded-by 'node -e "if(require(\"fs\").existsSync(\"src/domain.js\")){console.error(\"run_root_src_domain_leak\");process.exit(1)}" && cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer && npm run check:domain:assets && npm run check:domain:work-orders && npm test' max 4
    prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Repair workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js only. FAILED_CHECK: full domain contract tests. DO_NOT_TOUCH: workspace/fscrud-01/package.json, workspace/fscrud-01/CONTRACT.md, workspace/fscrud-01/__tests__/domain.contract.test.js, workspace/fscrud-01/data/seed.json. ACTION read_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, then write_file workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js. Preserve exact CommonJS exports and all passing behavior. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root. Critique: ${_review_critique}
    run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  end

  prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Finalize only workspace/fscrud-01/README.md, workspace/fscrud-01/run-manifest.json, and workspace/fscrud-01/verification-report.md. Be honest: record that this is the micro-contract-v2 diagnostic arm, local model is supplied by the runner, and verifier status is only known after the harness runs it. Keep code, tests, seed, package, contract, server, and UI unchanged. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root.
  review strict criteria: "Final public checks and tests must pass; the hidden FSCRUD verifier is run only by the experiment harness after the flow." grounded-by 'node -e "if(require(\"fs\").existsSync(\"src/domain.js\")){console.error(\"run_root_src_domain_leak\");process.exit(1)}" && cd workspace/fscrud-01 && npm run check:domain:exports && npm run check:domain:customer && npm run check:domain:assets && npm run check:domain:work-orders && npm test' max 2
    prompt: Work only in ${fscrud_workspace}. Treat ${fscrud_workspace} as the app root. Repair only the file directly named by the public check critique. Allowed files: workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js, workspace/fscrud-01/README.md, workspace/fscrud-01/run-manifest.json, workspace/fscrud-01/verification-report.md. Never edit workspace/fscrud-01/__tests__, workspace/fscrud-01/package.json, workspace/fscrud-01/CONTRACT.md, workspace/fscrud-01/DOMAIN_API.md, workspace/fscrud-01/contracts/domain-exports.json, or workspace/fscrud-01/data/seed.json. Do not create or edit ./src/* at the run root. Critique: ${_review_critique}
    run: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const cp=require('child_process');const paths=['experiments/fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs','../../../../../fullstack-crud-comparison/scaffold/normalize-domain-export-surface.cjs'];const script=paths.find((p)=>fs.existsSync(p));if(!script){console.error('normalizer script missing');process.exit(1)}const r=cp.spawnSync(process.execPath,[script,'workspace/fscrud-01'],{stdio:'inherit'});process.exit(r.status??1)" [timeout 60]
  end

  run: node -e "require('fs').writeFileSync('workspace/fscrud-01/.pl-micro-contract-v2-complete','ok\n')" [timeout 60]

done when:
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/package.json
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/CONTRACT.md
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/DOMAIN_API.md
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/contracts/domain-exports.json
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-exports.cjs
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-customer.cjs
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-assets.cjs
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/scripts/check-domain-work-orders.cjs
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/README.md
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/src/domain.js
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/src/server.js
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/public/index.html
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/__tests__/domain.contract.test.js
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/data/seed.json
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/run-manifest.json
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/verification-report.md
  file_exists workspace/fscrud-01/.pl-micro-contract-v2-complete
